      <textAnnotation id="sid-E10F4B80-4A66-4A97-9D2C-BDE8E07D2D83" signavio:alignment="left" textFormat="text/plain">
         <extensionElements>
            <signavio:signavioMetaData metaKey="bordercolor" metaValue="#000000"/>
         </extensionElements>
         <text>The tax journal entry is recorded and the ending balances in the tax accounts are tied out to supporting work papers and reviewed by the designated global tax accountant before finalizing the SEC disclosures</text>
      </textAnnotation>
      <textAnnotation id="sid-E48CE443-DCD3-419B-81C0-A245684AAA7E" signavio:alignment="left" textFormat="text/plain">
         <extensionElements>
            <signavio:signavioMetaData metaKey="bordercolor" metaValue="#000000"/>
         </extensionElements>
         <text>The footnote is drafted by the TAG and reviewed by the designated global tax accountant</text>
      </textAnnotation>
      <textAnnotation id="sid-11DE564E-7CC9-4910-B82F-3A6A6441A42C" signavio:alignment="left">
